  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Cigarettes worth 19 lakhs are seized",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Police Special Task Force, a person was arrested in Maligawatta area with a stock of cigarettes worth over 19 lakh rupees, which were smuggled into Sri Lanka without duty.",
        "The police have taken more than 30,000 cigarettes with the suspect.",
        "The raid was carried out according to information received by the officers of the Organized Crime Unit of the Police Special Task Force.",
        "The police officers who conducted the raid said that the government pictorial warning was not written on these cigarettes. The 54-year-old suspect, a resident of Maligawatta area, has been handed over to the Maligawatta police for further investigation."
      ],
